Cindy Robbins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cindy_Robbins 0 Cynthia Chenault (born January 5, 1937) is an American television actress and producer/writer active from the mid-1950s to the present. She used the screen name Cindy Robbins in her acting credits.
